            %li{style: "color:#6383a5; list-style-type: none; list-style-image: url('http://dreamcatcher.net/images/icons/journal-24-hover.png')"}
              use as your multi-media diary and <b style="color: #0b3f6f;">journal</b>



          %h2{style: "color: #0b3f6f; font-size: 24px; font-weight: normal; margin: 0px"} using Dreamcatcher

          %ul{style: "font-size: 19px;"}

            %li{style: "color:#6383a5; list-style-type: none; list-style-image: url('http://dreamcatcher.net/images/icons/dream-24-hover.png')"}
